---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Innovation Framework - iNNv0" 
  description="Comprehensive early-stage innovation management framework with Design and Execution dimensions."
>
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-accent-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          Innovation Management <span class="gradient-text">Framework</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A comprehensive approach to building innovation capacity through strategic design and tactical execution.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Framework Overview -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-12 mb-12 scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Solution Structure</h2>
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>Modular Work Units:</strong> Self-contained building blocks you can plug into existing workflows or run as standalone sprints.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Inputs:</strong> Key documents, concepts, and tools such as strategic plans, customer personas, and ideation templates.</li>
            <li><strong>Tasks:</strong>
              <ul class="ml-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Autonomous exercises:</strong> Pre-recorded videos and guided worksheets for self-paced work.</li>
                <li><strong>Guided workshops:</strong> Live or virtual sessions led by our innovation coaches to deepen learning and collaboration.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Outputs:</strong> Tangible deliverables like opportunity maps, idea scorecards, prototype schematics, and user-test summaries.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Process Flow -->
      <div class="mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our Process Flow</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Self-Diagnostic (AI-Guided)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Method:</strong> Online chatbot questionnaire assessing current innovation capabilities.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Focus:</strong> Measures risk tolerance, leadership buy-in, resource allocation, and generates a personalized report.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Initial Diagnosis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Method:</strong> Facilitated discovery session mapping existing processes and pain points.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverable:</strong> Current State & Opportunity Map showing high-impact areas.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              3
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Idea Generation & Evaluation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Activities:</strong> Guided brainstorming followed by weighted scoring of ideas.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverable:</strong> Ranked Idea Backlog with rationale and estimated benefits.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              4
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Prototype Conceptualization</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Method:</strong> Rapid design sprint to sketch and storyboard key features.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Low-fidelity mock-ups and user journey sketches.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              5
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Validation & Feedback</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Activities:</strong> User interviews and usability tests capturing data.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverable:</strong> Feedback & Insights Report with actionable recommendations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-glow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white font-bold text-xl">
              6
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Iteration & Refinement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Continuous improvement through lean cycles.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverable:</strong> Refined Prototype & Next Steps Plan for scaling.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Methodologies -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-12 scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Integration with Best-Practice Methodologies</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-check text-primary-600"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">24 Steps of Disciplined Entrepreneurship</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">End-to-end framework for building a scalable venture from idea to launch.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-check text-primary-600"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Lean Startup</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Build–Measure–Learn cycles emphasizing quick experiments and data-driven decisions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-check text-primary-600"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Running Lean</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Rapid hypothesis validation to align teams on assumptions, risks, and metrics.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-check text-primary-600"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Design Thinking</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Empathize → Define → Ideate → Prototype → Test for human-centered solutions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
